k/upload/product/original/167416769834.膨脹PU膠4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.5metal.com.hk%2Fupload%2Fproduct%2Foriginal%2F167416769834.%E8%86%A8%E8%84%B9PU%E8%86%A04.jpg&h=b5e0d294&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.5metal.com.hk/editor_upload_image/images/膨脹PU膠3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.5metal.com.hk%2Feditor_upload_image%2Fimages%2F%E8%86%A8%E8%84%B9PU%E8%86%A03.jpg&h=1843ed82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/i2/720462376/O1CN01aTeFTM1TQFYZVXJKJ_!!720462376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fi2%2F720462376%2FO1CN01aTeFTM1TQFYZVXJKJ_%21%21720462376.jpg&h=e5626c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n膨脹PU膠描述 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">TYL-泡沫S被修改單組分聚氨酯泡沫填充或接縫和間隙密封</span>。泡沫噴出後迅速膨脹並迅速與空氣中的水分反應固化成精細的蜂窩結構泡沫。它<span style=\"color: red;\">形成了一個強有力的鍵合最建築材料</span>，如混凝土表面上。 TYL-泡沫S被在噴嘴增壓級氣霧罐供應。<br />\n <br />\n膨脹PU膠用途 :<br />\n‧腔填充 <br />\n‧在車頂結構的所有開口密封 <br />\n‧聲學障板的應用 <br />\n‧吸音層的應用 <br />\n‧安裝窗戶和門框 <br />\n <br />\n膨脹PU膠優點 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">‧高灌裝能力 </span><br />\n‧高絕緣值，熱學和聲學 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">‧很好的粘結性能 <br />\n‧卓越的穩定性不收縮或膨脹後 </span><br />\n‧無氟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>復活彩蛋</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bZyV8M4.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"62cde08299c26eb898dd1827491d272d695e9c54","tid":1649913,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:02:43.000Z","msg":"「整合」夢遊生存指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0dc682b92cde8a20eb106040e8e7a3511289dd96","tid":1649913,"uid":155263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:03:08.000Z","msg":"推到文宣組見到(16/10)<br />\n如果片主見到希望唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"